 26/2/18 Sell Up earli and saw A.Co off to the Lottinghen rifl rang , Then met the Coy Command at my billet at 9 a.m. and discuss the Battalion tactic scheme with them . We rode out to the ground abov Quesqu ? a pleasant ride and a love morn . Went over the ground and allot the frontag c. We then met the Battalion in column of rout with the Band and march through ESCOUEVILLES out on to the main road to Corlett . This is a splendid Nation Road and straight as a die . We went right through the wood befor Corlettt and pull up for lunch on a green field
